"Almost every family in America faces a mental health challenge at some point, and my family is no exception. We must remove the stigma and continue to educate ourselves so that we see the signs when someone is struggling and are empowered to offer support. And we can and will save lives by doing so.” - Kendra Scott

Go behind the design with our VP of Creative Design, Leah Lucas, to learn more about the inspiration for our Sun & Moon Charm, benefiting mental health causes. ☀️🌙✨

node.title: Behind the Design of Our Charm Benefiting Mental Health Causes ☀️🌙✨

node.text:
Moms have been through a lot this past year. This Mother's Day, we committed to giving 50 moms a $2,000 PTO Fund to help support personal time off just for them and their mental health. We told a few of our finalists that our judges wanted to ask them some questions... But really, they were about to get the surprise of a lifetime with a call from Kendra & @busyphilipps .

Wear Life Beautifully. #WearItLikeAMom
